title: Why is akali a man now?

replies.body: I love the preference conversation because you can always tell the sheltered suburban kid _immediately_.  Comments like "She looks like she smells" or "She has thunder thighs!" is a dead giveaway that you're in the 18-24 year old demographic, and you don't know what adult women look like.
